WEBVTT

03:33.280 --> 03:37.200
I think you can go down. There are lots of seats still vacant.

05:09.160 --> 05:13.240
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

05:18.160 --> 05:20.320
At the very outset

05:20.520 --> 05:24.920
I have to tell you that truth is what it is.

05:26.480 --> 05:32.280
You cannot transform it, change it

05:32.520 --> 05:39.440
and unfortunately at this human awareness you cannot know it.

05:44.160 --> 05:47.600
Now whatever I am going to tell you today,

05:47.800 --> 05:51.520
you need not believe blind folded. We have already

05:51.760 --> 05:56.200
suffered a lot because of blind faith.

05:56.400 --> 05:59.560
But if it is proved

05:59.760 --> 06:03.120
then as honest people you have to accept it.

06:04.560 --> 06:09.560
Because it is for the benevolence of your being,

06:09.760 --> 06:14.920
for the benevolence of your society,

06:15.120 --> 06:20.680
your city, your country and the world at large.

06:23.240 --> 06:25.960
So one has to understand

06:26.160 --> 06:32.240
that we have not known so far the Absolute Truth.

06:32.440 --> 06:35.000
If we had known the Absolute Truth

06:35.200 --> 06:38.960
there would not have been any problem whatsoever.

06:40.720 --> 06:44.520
Because everybody would see the same truth.

06:44.720 --> 06:48.280
There cannot be so many [dead] dogmas,

06:48.480 --> 06:52.760
so many discussions, arguments, fights and wars.

06:52.960 --> 07:00.120
If everybody sees the same point then who will fight?

07:00.320 --> 07:04.000
For example I am sitting before you, you all see it clearly

07:04.240 --> 07:05.240
and you know it.

07:05.440 --> 07:08.920
So you are not going to fight that I am here or not.

07:10.720 --> 07:16.320
For that we need a last breakthrough of our evolution.

07:16.520 --> 07:21.640
As human beings, still, we have freedom to think whatever we like

07:21.840 --> 07:27.600
but we haven’t got capacity to know the Absolute Truth.

07:27.800 --> 07:30.760
If that is so and if there is a way out,

07:30.960 --> 07:34.120
why not we try for it?

07:34.320 --> 07:38.960
You have been already told about this,

07:40.760 --> 07:43.360
this instrument that is within you.

07:43.560 --> 07:48.600
I've never seen such a big one - today is the only...

07:52.920 --> 07:57.360
In Australia everything is big I tell you.

07:57.560 --> 07:59.520
Very nice.

07:59.720 --> 08:04.280
I mean it can cover a very big hall as we had yesterday.

08:04.480 --> 08:08.520
A day before we had three thousand three hundred people

08:08.720 --> 08:10.960
and this would have been better there.

08:11.160 --> 08:13.600
All right, as it is

08:13.800 --> 08:18.520
this is the subtle instrument that is within us.

08:18.720 --> 08:22.840
It's created through our evolutionary process.

08:25.200 --> 08:31.320
As we learn, say, science and other things

08:31.560 --> 08:34.960
from western countries, from Australia, from all

08:35.200 --> 08:38.840
Japanese countries and all that.

08:39.040 --> 08:43.920
We can see the civilization has grown so big

08:44.120 --> 08:49.000
and we do not know our roots.

08:49.200 --> 08:54.880
That’s why, what is happening is, people are waiting for a shock.

08:55.080 --> 08:58.240
Already they are very much upset.

08:58.440 --> 09:02.400
What has gone wrong with us that we should know our roots?

09:02.600 --> 09:06.800
Now if these roots are coming from East or from India

09:07.000 --> 09:11.120
why should we abhor it,

09:11.320 --> 09:13.920
why should we condemn it?

09:14.120 --> 09:15.960
Because it's very important

09:16.160 --> 09:18.320
that we have to seek our roots

09:18.520 --> 09:21.400
and this is the knowledge of the roots.

09:25.520 --> 09:30.040
The human problems

09:30.240 --> 09:34.440
actually cover all the global problems, most of it.

09:34.640 --> 09:39.920
And to solve them

09:40.120 --> 09:47.320
we have to see to this inner subtle instrument within us.

09:47.520 --> 09:52.200
When these centers are in jeopardy,

09:52.400 --> 09:55.960
then we get physical, mental, emotional, spiritual,

09:56.160 --> 09:58.960
social, political, all problems -

09:59.160 --> 10:02.960
because problems are caused by human beings

10:03.200 --> 10:07.000
and human beings are in trouble because of these centers.

10:08.040 --> 10:11.760
So if by chance,

10:11.960 --> 10:15.080
you know how to correct your centers

10:15.280 --> 10:19.000
and then to correct others' centers also,

10:19.200 --> 10:22.200
you solve the problem.

10:22.400 --> 10:25.960
Now this power that is being told as ‘Kundalini’,

10:26.160 --> 10:28.160
is called ‘Kundalini’ because

10:28.360 --> 10:32.600
‘Kundal’ means coils - it is coiled three and a half times.

10:32.800 --> 10:35.360
It has some mathematical calculation.

10:37.280 --> 10:39.400
Now this ‘Kundalini’ when She is awakened

10:39.600 --> 10:42.000
She passes through these centers

10:42.200 --> 10:45.320
and She enlightens them.

10:45.520 --> 10:49.200
She nourishes them and She integrates.

10:49.400 --> 10:54.520
Ultimately She pierces through your fontanel bone area -

10:54.720 --> 10:58.800
in Sanskrit we call it ‘Brahmarandra’ -pierces through

10:58.960 --> 11:05.160
and becomes one with this all pervading power.

11:05.360 --> 11:09.280
So you achieve two results.

11:09.480 --> 11:12.080
So the truth about you is that

11:12.280 --> 11:17.480
you are not this body, mind, your ego, your conditionings.

11:17.680 --> 11:19.400
Because you say this is my ego,

11:19.600 --> 11:22.760
this is my conditioning, this is my house,

11:22.960 --> 11:25.320
this is my wife, my husband.

11:25.520 --> 11:29.760
So this ’my’, who is the ‘my’ there?

11:29.960 --> 11:33.080
So you become the ‘I’, the ‘self’,

11:33.280 --> 11:36.920
that is the ‘Spirit’, which you are!

11:37.120 --> 11:40.880
And the second truth is that there is an All Pervading Power

11:41.080 --> 11:45.120
which does all the living work.

11:45.360 --> 11:50.520
Look at these beautiful flowers; it's a miracle, if you see?

11:50.720 --> 11:54.000
They are different flowers from different seeds of certain heights,

11:54.200 --> 11:57.280
certain shapes, certain colour

11:57.480 --> 12:00.840
and you take it for granted.

12:01.040 --> 12:06.400
You don’t even think about them how they have come out like that.

12:06.600 --> 12:09.960
Who runs our heart?

12:10.160 --> 12:12.440
The doctors will say: autonomous nervous system.

12:12.640 --> 12:15.640
But who is the ‘auto’?

12:15.840 --> 12:19.200
So we never question anything about living process,

12:19.400 --> 12:22.000
because we can’t answer.

12:22.200 --> 12:24.080
This living process

12:24.320 --> 12:28.400
is done by a very subtle energy,

12:28.600 --> 12:33.960
which we can call by any name,

12:34.160 --> 12:38.520
is the ‘divine power of love’.

12:38.720 --> 12:43.600
You can call it as ‘Ruh’ as in Koran,

12:43.800 --> 12:49.840
you can call it as ‘Brahmachaitanya’ as in Sanskrit

12:50.040 --> 12:56.520
and as ‘Ritambhara Pragya’ by Patanjali.

12:56.720 --> 12:59.480
You can give it any name to it, is different but,

12:59.800 --> 13:03.840
it is a power which we have never felt before

13:04.040 --> 13:09.600
which is a subtle power which does all living work.

13:09.800 --> 13:11.520
So, as if,

13:11.720 --> 13:16.560
if you have not reached that source of energy,

13:16.760 --> 13:22.360
the whole development outside is collapsing.

13:24.240 --> 13:27.640
Also, supposing this instrument

13:27.840 --> 13:31.000
is not connected to the mains,

13:31.200 --> 13:36.960
then, it has no identity, it has no meaning. Why was it created?

13:38.680 --> 13:42.800
And everywhere these days I find the seekers

13:42.960 --> 13:47.880
are trying to find out their identity.

13:48.080 --> 13:52.800
So what is your identity, is that you are the Spirit,

13:52.960 --> 13:56.880
you are the ‘Spirit’ and this Spirit

13:57.080 --> 14:04.440
is the ultimate that you have to become.

14:04.640 --> 14:06.880
Once you become the Spirit,

14:07.080 --> 14:09.680
in the light of the Spirit

14:09.880 --> 14:11.480
you see the Truth.

14:11.680 --> 14:14.120
First of all on your fingertips

14:14.320 --> 14:18.960
you start feeling this cool breeze,

14:19.160 --> 14:21.200
‘cool breeze of the Holy Ghost’, you can call it

14:21.400 --> 14:25.240
or this ‘All pervading power of Divine Love’.

14:25.440 --> 14:29.560
And when you start feeling that power,

14:29.800 --> 14:33.200
is... your body acts like a computer.

14:33.400 --> 14:35.760
You ask any question.

14:35.960 --> 14:38.680
There are many people who don’t believe - there is no God.

14:38.880 --> 14:45.840
I think it is very unscientific to say there is no God,

14:46.040 --> 14:48.680
because you have not found out.

14:48.880 --> 14:52.440
Without finding out how can you say there is no God?

14:52.640 --> 14:56.160
They have all kinds of funny stories even about Christ.

14:56.360 --> 15:01.480
They say He was not the son of God. How do you say?

15:01.680 --> 15:05.600
You are not at that point where you can decide,

15:05.800 --> 15:07.600
what is true, what is not.

15:07.800 --> 15:09.840
Just mental projections,

15:10.040 --> 15:14.520
they go on condemning all the great incarnations, and

15:14.720 --> 15:17.960
all the great prophets, and seers and sages

15:18.160 --> 15:20.120
because they are all blind.

15:20.320 --> 15:24.640
Kabira says that, "O God, how am I to explain

15:24.800 --> 15:27.720
to all these people who are blind in this world?"

15:27.920 --> 15:32.120
Kaise samaja hu, sab jagah andha (Hindi to be checked).

15:32.320 --> 15:36.280
So, Sahaja means, ‘Saha” means born,

15:38.360 --> 15:40.520
‘saha’ means ‘with’, ‘ja’  ’born’.

15:40.720 --> 15:43.080
Born with you is the right

15:43.280 --> 15:47.800
to become a ‘yogi’, to have this union, ‘yoga’

15:47.960 --> 15:49.480
with the Divine.

15:49.680 --> 15:53.480
And it is very simple now.

15:53.680 --> 15:58.000
In the modern times it's very simple.

15:58.200 --> 16:01.960
In the olden days there were people

16:02.240 --> 16:07.960
who were trying to give Realization, Self-Realization,

16:08.200 --> 16:12.920
but they would have one or two disciples only.

16:15.160 --> 16:17.680
And will...

16:17.880 --> 16:21.920
they would not reveal the secrets about the ‘Kundalini’,

16:22.120 --> 16:25.720
so clearly.

16:25.920 --> 16:28.720
In the twelfth century

16:28.920 --> 16:31.920
one great poet called Gyaneshwara,

16:32.120 --> 16:34.640
he asked permission from his master -

16:34.840 --> 16:39.560
his own brother was his master - that, "Allow me to talk about it.

16:39.760 --> 16:42.200
And I will not do anything

16:42.400 --> 16:44.600
but I'll just talk about it in my book,

16:44.800 --> 16:47.000
‘Gyaneshwari’.

16:47.200 --> 16:51.680
In the sixth chapter He wrote very clearly about it.

16:51.880 --> 16:57.480
In Sanskrit we had, fourteen thousand years back

16:57.680 --> 17:00.760
a great Markendeya who had written about it.

17:00.960 --> 17:05.160
Sixth century also ‘Adi Shankaracharya’ wrote about it.

17:05.360 --> 17:09.800
But it was all in Sanskrit, was not available to common people.

17:10.000 --> 17:11.360
After this,

17:11.560 --> 17:13.560
after the twelfth century

17:13.760 --> 17:17.200
when he (Gyaneshwara) wrote it, the people who were in charge of religion

17:17.400 --> 17:18.920
said that this is a

17:19.120 --> 17:22.360
‘nishiddha’, means is something not to be read by anyone,

17:22.560 --> 17:24.800
it's not, because they didn’t know what to do about it.

17:24.960 --> 17:27.080
They had no idea, they had no knowledge.

17:27.320 --> 17:29.720
They had no knowledge about the Divine

17:29.920 --> 17:34.680
and they were in charge of religion, maybe making money.

17:34.880 --> 17:36.880
So the second...

17:39.080 --> 17:42.840
lot of people, saints came up in India

17:43.040 --> 17:44.640
In the sixteenth century

17:44.840 --> 17:47.160
who have talked about it,

17:47.360 --> 17:50.600
all over the country, about this ‘Kundalini’.

17:50.800 --> 17:52.480
In the Bible also it is written

17:52.680 --> 17:55.160
that I will appear before you like ‘tongues of flames’,

17:55.360 --> 17:56.960
and these look like tongues of flames,

17:57.200 --> 17:58.760
very silent, beautiful.

17:58.960 --> 18:04.960
In these colors as shown here, they look like.

18:05.200 --> 18:09.320
And some people have described them, those who have been

18:09.520 --> 18:12.720
moving round the circle.

18:12.920 --> 18:15.120
But, to enter into it, to be -

18:15.320 --> 18:20.120
supposing I see the light, I am not the light.

18:20.320 --> 18:23.200
This is the point many people have missed,

18:23.400 --> 18:28.240
that you have to be not to see something.

18:28.440 --> 18:31.240
And once you become

18:31.440 --> 18:34.920
then you have so many powers within you

18:35.120 --> 18:37.240
that you start manifesting them.

18:37.480 --> 18:38.920
The other day there were some these

18:39.120 --> 18:41.160
‘born again’ people were just...

18:41.400 --> 18:44.280
like mad, were there shouting, shouting.

18:44.480 --> 18:48.640
I said, "You are not 'born again', what are you doing?"

18:48.840 --> 18:52.560
You just call themselves ‘born again’, is not the way.

18:52.760 --> 18:55.440
As we call ourselves Hindus, Muslims, Christians, this -

18:55.640 --> 18:58.840
we are not!

18:59.040 --> 19:00.880
We are really not because

19:01.080 --> 19:04.720
anybody can commit any mistake,

19:04.920 --> 19:06.120
can commit any sin -

19:06.320 --> 19:10.320
you may belong to any religion.

19:10.520 --> 19:14.800
So there's something missing within you and your religion.

19:15.000 --> 19:19.440
It is not innately manifesting within you.

19:19.640 --> 19:22.320
And that's the point we have to be

19:22.520 --> 19:24.760
honest about it.

19:24.960 --> 19:28.560
That our religion and ourselves

19:28.760 --> 19:33.040
are not one with ourselves.

19:33.240 --> 19:36.040
As we can see something,

19:36.240 --> 19:39.240
are we righteous?

19:39.440 --> 19:45.120
Innately are we righteous? We are not.

19:45.320 --> 19:48.720
And there are temptations and temptations,

19:48.920 --> 19:51.520
so what’s wrong?

19:51.720 --> 19:53.200
We do all kinds of

19:53.440 --> 19:55.800
things and as far as the religion is concerned,

19:55.960 --> 19:57.560
still what you find

19:57.760 --> 20:02.560
that the religion is not one with us.

20:02.760 --> 20:04.600
And so many bad things are happening,

20:04.800 --> 20:06.720
you see these Muslims being killed here,

20:06.920 --> 20:09.560
these Israelis are being killed and this, I mean

20:09.760 --> 20:11.960
it is really I can’t understand

20:12.200 --> 20:15.960
how can you do it in the name of God.

20:17.880 --> 20:20.760
Now this Bosnia problem is there and people are

20:20.960 --> 20:23.560
dying and eating each other’s body,

20:23.760 --> 20:26.880
that sort of thing. I mean, can you imagine in modern times

20:27.080 --> 20:29.040
such things are happening all over the world?

20:29.240 --> 20:32.480
And it disturbs you completely -

20:32.680 --> 20:35.440
that "Why is it they don’t want to see the point?"

20:35.640 --> 20:39.680
There's something missing.

20:39.880 --> 20:45.120
With all that we have to understand that

20:45.320 --> 20:50.440
if we have to solve the problem of religion,

20:50.640 --> 20:53.760
one thing we must know, that all these religions

20:53.960 --> 20:57.680
were born on the same tree of spirituality.

20:57.880 --> 20:59.960
Only we have plucked the flowers.

21:00.200 --> 21:07.480
and now we are fighting with the dead flowers.

21:07.680 --> 21:09.000
Then where is the religion?

21:09.200 --> 21:13.560
Religion is this part that is shown as the green colour.

21:13.760 --> 21:16.520
You see the ten petals, the Ten commandments,

21:16.720 --> 21:22.840
ten petals. And this is to be awakened.

21:23.040 --> 21:27.280
That's only possible if this ‘Kundalini’ rises.

21:27.480 --> 21:30.320
She is your own power.

21:30.520 --> 21:33.600
She is your own individual mother.

21:33.800 --> 21:37.680
She has recorded everything within Herself,

21:37.880 --> 21:40.880
what you have been doing, what was your past

21:41.080 --> 21:43.280
and what are your problems

21:43.480 --> 21:45.600
and what are your conditionings.

21:45.800 --> 21:48.200
All your ventures She knows.

21:48.400 --> 21:50.400
It's like a tape recorder.

21:50.600 --> 21:51.640
But She's your mother

21:51.840 --> 21:54.960
and She is anxious to give you your second birth,

21:55.160 --> 21:59.000
very anxious, because these are some special times.

21:59.200 --> 22:01.080
I call them Blossom Time.

22:01.280 --> 22:05.560
In the Bible they say it is ‘Last Judgment’

22:05.760 --> 22:08.400
and in the Koran it is called ‘Khayyama’,

22:08.600 --> 22:11.960
is the resurrection time - whatever you may call it.

22:12.200 --> 22:14.960
This is a special time when you are born

22:15.200 --> 22:17.600
and you are all seekers, you are born

22:17.800 --> 22:19.680
to seek the Truth.

22:19.880 --> 22:22.240
Be honest about it

22:22.440 --> 22:26.600
that we have not yet achieved what we wanted

22:26.800 --> 22:29.040
out of whatever religion we follow,

22:29.240 --> 22:32.600
whatever way we worship God.

22:32.800 --> 22:36.960
Some people have some sort of satisfaction

22:37.200 --> 22:40.200
that, "No, no, no, Mother, we are very happy we have got this...

22:40.400 --> 22:43.640
No, that's not so.

22:43.840 --> 22:46.040
With this happening,

22:46.240 --> 22:48.880
the first thing happens to you that

22:49.080 --> 22:54.360
you develop a new dimension in your, your awareness.

22:54.560 --> 23:01.120
Just now you are not even conscious of your centers.

23:01.320 --> 23:04.320
Then you know your centers on your fingertips,

23:04.600 --> 23:07.480
you can feel them also inside.

23:07.680 --> 23:09.600
Like somebody will come and tell Me, "Mother,

23:09.800 --> 23:12.920
my ‘Agnya’ is caught. Please clear it out.

23:13.120 --> 23:15.960
Meaning what? "I am very egoistical.

23:16.160 --> 23:17.400
My ego is troubling me."

23:17.600 --> 23:21.520
Nobody would say that normally.

23:21.720 --> 23:25.520
Nobody will even think he has ego.

23:25.720 --> 23:28.400
But with this, you get separated

23:28.600 --> 23:31.680
from yourself and you see yourself

23:31.880 --> 23:35.400
and your problems.

23:35.600 --> 23:37.520
So the first thing happens to you,

23:37.720 --> 23:40.680
that you have self-knowledge.

23:40.880 --> 23:43.560
And the second thing then happens to you,

23:43.760 --> 23:46.760
that you have the knowledge of others.

23:46.960 --> 23:50.200
That is the ‘collective consciousness’,

23:50.400 --> 23:54.560
in which sitting down here you can find out

23:54.760 --> 23:56.960
whose chakras are catching where,

23:57.160 --> 24:00.120
what's happening where, what's wrong with somebody.

24:00.320 --> 24:02.320
But you don’t talk the language

24:02.520 --> 24:05.480
as we talk about, "Oh, this one is a corrupt man

24:05.680 --> 24:08.320
or he is just like that, he has this problem".

24:08.520 --> 24:10.840
No, we talk on chakras only.

24:11.040 --> 24:13.880
This is what the disciples of Christ were talking,

24:14.080 --> 24:15.960
the language of chakras.

24:16.160 --> 24:18.680
You say that "this person has this problem,

24:18.880 --> 24:21.320
this person has this problem".

24:21.520 --> 24:26.640
And you start not criticizing, telling him anything,

24:26.840 --> 24:29.320
but if you know how to correct your chakras,

24:29.520 --> 24:32.640
you can correct yours and you can correct others.

24:32.840 --> 24:36.120
This is the power you get which I call it as the

24:36.320 --> 24:38.800
‘collective consciousness’.

24:38.960 --> 24:43.440
Because who is the other?

24:43.640 --> 24:45.640
Is what we say,

24:45.840 --> 24:49.600
the ‘microcosm’ becomes the ‘macrocosm’.

24:49.800 --> 24:54.120
The one drop becomes the ocean.

24:54.320 --> 24:58.840
The consciousness of the ocean comes within.

24:59.040 --> 25:04.160
This is what is just waiting at your threshold.

25:04.360 --> 25:06.880
You can get it.

25:07.120 --> 25:12.080
It's very easy because it’s your own power

25:12.280 --> 25:14.480
and it manifests,

25:14.680 --> 25:17.960
so that you discover how glorious you are,

25:18.160 --> 25:21.160
how powerful you are.

25:21.360 --> 25:23.720
When this power starts flowing through you

25:23.920 --> 25:26.360
it corrects your chakras no doubt.

25:26.560 --> 25:28.600
But also

25:28.800 --> 25:33.480
in the light of your Spirit your attention becomes

25:33.680 --> 25:38.160
very innocent.

25:38.360 --> 25:41.640
Christ had said "Thou shall not have adulteress eyes".

25:41.880 --> 25:43.080
I would like to see

25:43.280 --> 25:45.840
any Christian nation where they don’t have

25:46.040 --> 25:52.560
people of this kind.

25:52.760 --> 25:54.440
So

25:54.640 --> 25:56.920
your attention becomes innocent

25:57.120 --> 25:59.920
and wherever you put your attention on,

26:00.120 --> 26:05.520
then what happens? It acts, it works.

26:05.720 --> 26:08.400
It works very well.

26:08.600 --> 26:13.760
So you become a global personality,

26:13.960 --> 26:15.360
universal personality.

26:15.560 --> 26:17.720
You can spread your attention.

26:17.920 --> 26:21.120
But you become so compassionate,

26:21.320 --> 26:24.600
so compassionate that you never think of harming anyone.

26:24.800 --> 26:27.600
But anything that is harming,

26:27.800 --> 26:31.160
you just put your attention and correct it

