They are the ones who killed small little children in the

46:20.120 --> 46:23.240
gas chamber and they saw them suffering.

46:23.440 --> 46:26.480
How could they do it?

46:26.680 --> 46:29.040
And they are supposed to be a very,

46:29.240 --> 46:31.240
what you call them,

46:31.440 --> 46:33.840
higher races. Max Muller says

46:34.040 --> 46:36.440
that they came to India and wrote ‘Vedas’.

46:36.640 --> 46:40.840
How can they write ‘Vedas’, these people?

46:41.040 --> 46:43.080
They are not afraid of God,

46:43.280 --> 46:45.960
the way they have behaved...

46:46.200 --> 46:49.760
But now Sahaja Yogis, the Sahaja Yogis Germans, you should say,

46:49.960 --> 46:53.760
the gentlest people you could think of, gentlest.

46:53.960 --> 46:56.920
They won’t hurt you, I mean, they are so beautiful.

46:57.160 --> 47:02.680
So this ‘Kundalini’ is the one, She cleanses all that,

47:02.880 --> 47:09.440
makes you peaceful, joyous and collective.

47:09.640 --> 47:15.080
Now I hope you all get your Realization tonight.

47:15.280 --> 47:17.440
Have faith in yourself - that's the main thing.

47:17.640 --> 47:21.720
You must have faith that you will all get Realization.

47:21.920 --> 47:25.120
I know there are people who have some questions also.

47:25.320 --> 47:28.120
These questions now I can answer - for the last

47:28.320 --> 47:31.040
twenty four years I have been doing this kind of work

47:31.240 --> 47:32.880
all over the world.

47:33.080 --> 47:34.080
So I can answer,

47:34.280 --> 47:37.680
because it's just a mental acrobat - I have become quite an expert.

47:37.880 --> 47:39.800
But it is of no use.

47:40.000 --> 47:44.760
By that thing you are not going to get to your Realization.

47:44.960 --> 47:48.560
What you have to ask really is your Self-Realization.

47:48.760 --> 47:54.160
This power is the power of pure desire.

47:54.360 --> 47:58.640
All other desires, as you know, in economics,

47:58.840 --> 48:02.160
that in general that they are not satiable.

48:02.360 --> 48:06.360
You may be aware, may not be aware, but this desire is within you,

48:06.560 --> 48:08.280
is to become the Spirit,

48:08.480 --> 48:10.880
to become one with this All Pervading Power

48:11.080 --> 48:14.560
and that acts, works and helps you.

48:14.760 --> 48:16.560
Everything is tangible.

48:16.760 --> 48:21.360
You will be amazed how it works,

48:21.560 --> 48:24.360
how it helps you!

48:24.560 --> 48:26.320
The second thing I have to tell you

48:26.520 --> 48:29.120
that it is not an individual thing.

48:29.320 --> 48:30.920
It is not that, you can say, "Oh!".

48:31.120 --> 48:32.960
First day you may feel very happy

48:33.200 --> 48:36.920
and very relaxed, on top of the world.

48:37.120 --> 48:39.200
That's not important.

48:39.400 --> 48:41.480
You have to come to the collective.

48:41.680 --> 48:43.280
You must understand

48:43.480 --> 48:46.960
the whole knowledge about your internal being

48:47.200 --> 48:51.720
and you have to be with the collective to grow.

48:51.920 --> 48:56.120
Like if I take out one, say

48:56.320 --> 48:59.920
nail out of my fingers, it will never grow.

49:00.120 --> 49:01.880
So it's the

49:02.080 --> 49:06.680
whole being, is a living organism.

49:06.880 --> 49:09.440
Only thing, you have to pay

49:09.640 --> 49:13.720
some time, as time... for it.

49:13.920 --> 49:18.000
They will tell you how to be in meditation, not to do meditation,

49:18.200 --> 49:21.320
how to be in meditation.

49:21.520 --> 49:24.520
So first you get the state of ‘thoughtless awareness’ -

49:24.720 --> 49:26.880
we call it as ‘Nirvichar Samadhi’.

49:27.080 --> 49:30.800
And then the state you get is called as ‘Nirvikalpa Samadhi’,

49:30.960 --> 49:34.040
where you get all the powers of raising others' ‘Kundalini’,

49:34.240 --> 49:36.960
giving them Realization, curing, everything.

49:37.200 --> 49:39.640
Those who have never come to the stage become orators.

49:39.840 --> 49:42.800
See these musicians singing Indian songs.

49:43.000 --> 49:44.880
Can you imagine this?

49:45.080 --> 49:48.080
I mean, English speaking people, so hard

49:48.280 --> 49:50.560
for Indian music, I tell you,

49:50.760 --> 49:53.080
especially for Indian words.

49:53.280 --> 49:54.800
But when they sing, ask Indians,

49:55.000 --> 49:57.640
they will tell you they sing like Indians...

49:57.840 --> 50:00.440
It was so difficult to teach even one word

50:00.640 --> 50:02.320
to the Englishmen in India -

50:02.520 --> 50:06.800
one word. And now you see this.

50:06.960 --> 50:08.440
What has happened to them?

50:08.640 --> 50:10.120
How suddenly they have picked up

50:10.320 --> 50:16.520
all the rhythm, all the thing, which is very difficult.

50:16.720 --> 50:18.560
So...

50:18.760 --> 50:20.800
all these powers which are within you,

50:20.960 --> 50:22.960
you have to manifest

50:23.160 --> 50:27.360
and enjoy your virtues, enjoy your virtues.

50:27.560 --> 50:31.320
You don’t become proud, but you enjoy them.

50:31.520 --> 50:33.560
You enjoy your generosity,

50:33.760 --> 50:35.680
enjoy your compassion,

50:35.880 --> 50:39.960
never feel that you are

50:40.200 --> 50:43.400
taking too much trouble, you are doing this and that, nothing.

50:43.600 --> 50:47.160
You think of others all the time and you live in peace

50:47.360 --> 50:49.440
and create peace all around.

50:49.640 --> 50:53.000
We have these people from sixty

50:53.200 --> 50:56.680
nations; they come to India once a year.

50:56.880 --> 51:01.200
I've never seen them quarrelling, fighting,

51:01.400 --> 51:05.840
doing anything against each other - never.

51:06.040 --> 51:10.040
How do they live from all different countries, from Chinese

51:10.240 --> 51:13.880
to Africans, from Africans to English

51:14.080 --> 51:18.200
and from English to Americans and Australians - so many?

51:18.400 --> 51:20.880
In Sydney we have twenty two centers.

51:21.080 --> 51:24.560
I must say Australia is one of our

51:24.760 --> 51:28.320
very great country which has really

51:28.520 --> 51:35.480
very enthusiastically has taken to Sahaja Yoga.

51:35.680 --> 51:38.600
And I am sure also you all will.

51:38.800 --> 51:42.280
We have a great story in our ‘Puranas’ about Australia

51:42.480 --> 51:44.840
which sometimes I'll tell you.

51:45.040 --> 51:47.080
So may God Bless you!

51:47.280 --> 51:52.600
And you be confident that you will have your Realization just now.

51:52.800 --> 51:57.280
You don’t have to do much - just it will take ten minutes more.

52:03.160 --> 52:06.320
But, of course, I respect your freedom.

52:06.520 --> 52:08.360
If you don’t want to have your Realization,

52:08.560 --> 52:11.480
you should leave the hall. I cannot force on you.

52:11.680 --> 52:13.960
It is something it cannot be forced.

52:14.160 --> 52:16.800
I respect your freedom out and out.

52:17.000 --> 52:20.200
So, if you want to go, you can go.

52:29.720 --> 52:34.120
All of you want Realization - it's very good.

52:38.160 --> 52:39.960
Now one thing that should not upset you,

52:40.160 --> 52:42.320
because I've seen people get upset if I tell them

52:42.520 --> 52:44.040
that you have to take out your shoes.

52:44.240 --> 52:47.480
I hope you won’t be upset with that.

52:53.040 --> 52:59.000
You need not take out your socks but your shoes.

52:59.200 --> 53:01.200
I does, sometimes.

53:16.120 --> 53:18.800
Don’t have to say any mantras, nothing,

53:19.040 --> 53:20.960
and you don’t have to concentrate also.

53:21.160 --> 53:24.440
Please don’t try to concentrate.

53:24.640 --> 53:27.800
Just keep yourself open.

53:27.960 --> 53:30.720
Don’t force yourself into anything.

53:30.920 --> 53:33.080
As I am saying, telling you that

53:33.280 --> 53:35.800
it has become so easy now -

53:36.000 --> 53:37.360
you don’t have to go to Himalayas

53:37.560 --> 53:39.960
and stand on your head or anything.

53:40.160 --> 53:42.400
You have to be very comfortable

53:42.600 --> 53:45.640
and also

53:45.840 --> 53:50.760
you should be very much pleasantly placed toward yourself.

53:50.960 --> 53:53.520
Because as I said, you are human beings,

53:53.720 --> 53:56.960
you are at the epitomy of evolution.

53:57.160 --> 54:01.880
And you are...  have a right to have this,

54:02.080 --> 54:07.240
because you are born at this time with a special purpose.

54:07.440 --> 54:09.600
So in no way you should condemn yourself.

54:09.800 --> 54:11.800
This is the first condition.

54:11.960 --> 54:16.680
Have full confidence.

54:16.880 --> 54:20.040
The another thing is you shouldn’t feel guilty at this time;

54:20.240 --> 54:22.600
please don’t feel guilty for anything.

54:22.800 --> 54:26.840
It has become a fashion now to feel guilty for anything.

54:27.040 --> 54:29.640
I mean, even, if supposing you spill some

54:29.840 --> 54:32.520
coffee you go on feeling guilty for your life.

54:32.720 --> 54:34.960
What's this going on?

54:35.160 --> 54:37.120
You must value yourself.

54:37.320 --> 54:39.360
This life is not meant

54:39.560 --> 54:42.880
for feeling bad for small, small things.

54:43.080 --> 54:47.160
It is very great, it’s very precious.

54:47.360 --> 54:48.920
So please don’t have any guilt.

54:49.120 --> 54:52.600
But if you have, then you catch on this center here.

54:52.800 --> 54:59.400
And this is such a dangerous thing because it gives you

54:59.600 --> 55:02.600
what we call as angina.

55:02.800 --> 55:07.840
It may give you spondylitis. It may give you very lethargic organs.

55:08.040 --> 55:10.480
So very dangerous is to feel guilt.

55:10.680 --> 55:12.800
So why feel guilty unnecessarily?

55:12.960 --> 55:16.520
I tell you if you were guilty, you would have been in jail.

55:16.720 --> 55:20.360
Now you are sitting here, so don’t feel guilty about

55:20.560 --> 55:22.320
anything whatsoever.

55:22.520 --> 55:26.640
I assure you, you are not guilty.

55:26.840 --> 55:34.120
So, you have to really forgive yourself.

55:34.320 --> 55:39.880
Now, the most simple condition is this

55:40.080 --> 55:44.360
that you have to forgive everyone.

55:44.560 --> 55:47.600
People might say it's very difficult to forgive.

55:47.800 --> 55:51.160
But, whether you forgive or not - I am telling the logic,

55:51.360 --> 55:54.600
now think about it - whether you forgive or not what do you do?

55:54.840 --> 55:57.280
I don’t do anything.

55:57.480 --> 56:01.520
But when you don’t forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

56:01.720 --> 56:06.440
Those who have troubled you, tortured you,

56:06.640 --> 56:08.000
are not feeling bad.

56:08.200 --> 56:11.960
But you are the one who is torturing yourself.

56:12.160 --> 56:15.760
But at this time, the problem is that this centre of Agnya

56:15.960 --> 56:21.080
which is like this, absolutely constructed like this, like a cross -

56:21.280 --> 56:23.560
it is on the optic chiasma -

56:23.760 --> 56:26.200
and if you don’t forgive, it won’t open at all.

56:26.400 --> 56:27.400
But if you forgive

56:27.600 --> 56:30.440
it will definitely open and the Kundalini will pass.

56:30.640 --> 56:33.960
So, at this juncture you as it is

56:34.200 --> 56:35.640
troubled yourself so much,

56:35.840 --> 56:37.880
at this juncture please,

56:38.080 --> 56:41.120
please forgive everyone in general.

56:41.320 --> 56:44.640
Don’t even think about them because it is a headache.

56:44.840 --> 56:47.680
It's a real headache even to think of these people.

56:47.880 --> 56:49.960
So you just forgive in general.

56:50.200 --> 56:54.320
Of course we'll tell you how to do it. It's very simple.

56:54.520 --> 56:58.120
Now to begin with you keep your eyes open,

56:58.320 --> 57:01.400
I'll show you how you have to

57:01.600 --> 57:08.040
yourself enrich your own centers - very simple.

57:08.240 --> 57:11.520
So please put your left hand towards Me like this comfortably.

57:11.720 --> 57:13.800
You have to be comfortable. That’s very important.

57:13.960 --> 57:15.920
Please both the feet apart from each other

57:16.120 --> 57:18.680
because these are two powers, left and right.

57:18.880 --> 57:22.880
Put your left hand towards Me on your lap,

57:23.080 --> 57:25.960
just like this.

57:26.200 --> 57:28.800
And now

57:28.960 --> 57:34.280
we have to use our left side with our right hand.

57:34.480 --> 57:39.920
Now please put your right hand on your heart.

57:40.120 --> 57:46.880
This is the center where the Spirit resides.

57:47.080 --> 57:48.680
If you become the Spirit,

57:48.880 --> 57:52.120
you become your own master in the light of the Spirit.

57:52.320 --> 57:54.640
So please take your right hand

57:54.880 --> 57:59.320
in the upper portion of your abdomen, on the liver.

57:59.520 --> 58:05.840
All of you should do it, please.

58:06.040 --> 58:08.400
This is the center of your mastery

58:08.640 --> 58:11.960
which is created by great prophets

58:12.160 --> 58:18.240
and seers and sages.

58:18.440 --> 58:21.720
Surprisingly the center of pure knowledge

58:21.920 --> 58:25.280
is lower here on the left hand side

58:25.480 --> 58:31.240
in the lower portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

58:31.440 --> 58:38.840
Whatever you have done, forget it, forget it.

58:39.040 --> 58:45.680
Now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen.

58:45.880 --> 58:52.040
Now on your heart.

58:52.240 --> 58:55.960
Now in the corner of your neck and shoulders.

58:56.160 --> 58:57.720
As I have already told you

58:57.920 --> 58:59.920
when this center catches what is the problem.

59:00.120 --> 59:06.440
Turn your head to your right, please.

59:06.640 --> 59:09.120
It’s very catching today.

59:09.320 --> 59:14.520
Please don’t feel guilty for anything. You must...

59:14.720 --> 59:19.760
There.

59:19.960 --> 59:23.360
Please take your right hand on top of your forehead across

59:23.560 --> 59:26.960
and bend your head slowly.

59:27.160 --> 59:31.440
We have to be humble about it, you see.

59:31.640 --> 59:38.320
So here you have to forgive everyone in general.

59:41.040 --> 59:46.120
Now take back your right hand on the backside of your head

59:46.320 --> 59:49.840
and push back your head as far as possible.

59:50.040 --> 59:54.880
Here,

59:55.080 --> 59:59.040
without counting your mistakes,

59:59.240 --> 01:00:02.680
without feeling guilty, just for your satisfaction,

01:00:02.880 --> 01:00:05.240
you will have to ask forgiveness

01:00:05.440 --> 01:00:11.520
from this All Pervading Power.

01:00:11.720 --> 01:00:16.640
Now please stretch your hand or palm fully.

01:00:16.840 --> 01:00:19.440
Now we go to the last center,

01:00:19.640 --> 01:00:22.040
so please put the centre of your palm

01:00:22.240 --> 01:00:25.360
on top of the fontanel bone area

01:00:25.560 --> 01:00:30.400
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:00:30.600 --> 01:00:35.160
Now please put down your head.

01:00:35.360 --> 01:00:37.120
Now push back your fingers nicely

01:00:37.320 --> 01:00:42.320
so there's a good pressure on your scalp.

01:00:42.520 --> 01:00:46.360
Now put down your head and you have to move, move the scalp

01:00:46.600 --> 01:00:51.080
seven times clockwise very slowly.

01:01:02.600 --> 01:01:05.200
That’s all we have to do actually.

01:01:05.400 --> 01:01:07.960
But remember you have to push back your fingers.

01:01:08.200 --> 01:01:11.160
Now you can take out your spectacles

01:01:11.360 --> 01:01:13.240
because you have to close your eyes.

01:01:13.440 --> 01:01:16.320
It might help also your eyesight.

01:01:16.520 --> 01:01:19.680
Please,

01:01:19.920 --> 01:01:21.920
before closing I must tell you again

01:01:22.120 --> 01:01:23.920
that please put both the

01:01:24.120 --> 01:01:26.560
legs apart from each other

01:01:26.760 --> 01:01:30.440
and the left hand

01:01:30.640 --> 01:01:36.840
towards Me on your lap comfortably in any way that you like.

01:01:37.040 --> 01:01:41.840
And then now place your right hand on your heart.

01:01:45.440 --> 01:01:49.320
Here, I've told you resides the Spirit.

01:01:49.520 --> 01:01:52.400
You have to ask Me

01:01:52.600 --> 01:01:56.880
a very fundamental question about yourself in your heart.

01:01:57.080 --> 01:02:02.400
So please,

01:02:02.600 --> 01:02:06.440
ask in your heart, three times.

01:02:06.640 --> 01:02:10.480
You can call me ‘Mother’ or ‘Shri Mataji’ whatever you like.

01:02:10.680 --> 01:02:13.880
“Mother, am I the Spirit?”

01:02:14.080 --> 01:02:15.960
Ask this question three times in your heart.

01:02:16.200 --> 01:02:20.280
"Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:02:31.240 --> 01:02:33.760
Now, I've told you if you become the ‘Spirit’,

01:02:33.960 --> 01:02:37.480
you become your own master.

01:02:37.680 --> 01:02:39.680
So now take down your right hand

01:02:39.880 --> 01:02:41.880
in the upper portion of your abdomen

01:02:42.080 --> 01:02:44.840
on the left hand side.

01:02:46.080 --> 01:02:50.400
Here,

01:02:50.600 --> 01:02:53.520
you have to ask another fundamental question.

01:02:53.720 --> 01:02:59.960
“Mother, am I my master?”

01:03:00.200 --> 01:03:05.200
Ask this question three times.

01:03:09.560 --> 01:03:12.720
I have already told you

01:03:12.920 --> 01:03:16.280
that I respect your freedom.

01:03:16.480 --> 01:03:18.640
And I cannot force

01:03:18.840 --> 01:03:24.240
divine pure knowledge on you.

01:03:24.440 --> 01:03:25.920
So now

01:03:26.160 --> 01:03:27.960
please take your right hand

01:03:28.160 --> 01:03:33.040
in the lower portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

01:03:33.240 --> 01:03:40.160
Here,

01:03:40.400 --> 01:03:42.600
you have to ask six times,

01:03:42.800 --> 01:03:46.840
because this center has got six petals,

01:03:47.040 --> 01:03:53.800
“Mother, please give me pure knowledge”,

01:03:53.960 --> 01:03:59.320
or you can say, “Mother please give me divine pure knowledge”.

01:03:59.520 --> 01:04:04.920
Whatever is divine is pure.

01:04:05.120 --> 01:04:07.680
Six times.

01:04:07.880 --> 01:04:10.800
As soon as you start asking

01:04:11.000 --> 01:04:13.080
for pure divine knowledge,

01:04:13.280 --> 01:04:17.840
the ‘Kundalini’ starts rising like a primule.

01:04:18.040 --> 01:04:23.160
Now we have to

01:04:23.360 --> 01:04:26.840
open our higher centers

01:04:27.040 --> 01:04:31.600
by our self-confidence,

01:04:31.800 --> 01:04:34.240
for the Kundalini to pass through.

01:04:34.440 --> 01:04:36.680
Now, take your right hand -

01:04:36.880 --> 01:04:39.080
you are working only on the left hand side -

01:04:39.280 --> 01:04:40.360
in the upper portion

01:04:40.560 --> 01:04:42.600
of your abdomen, on the left hand side.

01:04:42.800 --> 01:04:45.280
Press it hard.

01:04:45.480 --> 01:04:52.440
Now, here with full confidence, please say ten times,

01:04:52.640 --> 01:04:56.040
“Mother, I am my own master”.

01:04:56.240 --> 01:04:58.080
The Kundalini wants

01:04:58.280 --> 01:05:01.960
you to show yourself confidence.

01:05:07.200 --> 01:05:11.960
Please say it ten times.

01:05:12.160 --> 01:05:14.760
At the very outset, I've told you

01:05:14.960 --> 01:05:17.600
that the truth is that you are not this body,

01:05:17.800 --> 01:05:20.240
this mind, this ego, these feelings,

01:05:20.440 --> 01:05:23.240
these emotions, these conditionings,

01:05:23.440 --> 01:05:30.800
but you are the pure Spirit.

01:05:30.960 --> 01:05:35.440
So, now raise your right hand on top of your heart.

01:05:35.640 --> 01:05:40.480
And here you have to say again with full self-confidence,

01:05:40.680 --> 01:05:45.120
“Mother, I am the pure Spirit”.

01:05:45.320 --> 01:05:46.720
Please say it.

01:05:46.920 --> 01:05:49.160
Please say it twelve times,

01:05:49.360 --> 01:05:54.520
“Mother I am the pure Spirit”.

01:05:59.000 --> 01:06:00.920
I have already told you

01:06:01.160 --> 01:06:04.560
that this All Pervading Power

01:06:04.760 --> 01:06:08.280
is the ocean of knowledge,

01:06:08.480 --> 01:06:10.480
ocean of compassion,

01:06:10.680 --> 01:06:16.080
ocean of blessings, but above all it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:16.280 --> 01:06:20.160
And whatever mistakes you might have committed,

01:06:20.360 --> 01:06:24.320
are easily dissolved by this ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:24.520 --> 01:06:26.200
So forgive yourself.

01:06:26.400 --> 01:06:27.720
And put your right hand

01:06:27.920 --> 01:06:30.480
in the corner of your neck and shoulder

01:06:30.680 --> 01:06:34.560
and turn your head to your right.

01:06:34.800 --> 01:06:36.880
Here,

01:06:37.080 --> 01:06:39.280
with full confidence again,

01:06:39.480 --> 01:06:43.120
you have to say sixteen times,

01:06:43.320 --> 01:06:46.800
“Mother, I am not guilty at all”,

01:06:47.000 --> 01:06:50.440
“Mother I am not guilty at all”. Please say this.

01:06:50.640 --> 01:06:52.560
Is very important because this center

01:06:52.760 --> 01:06:57.640
is catching very much tonight here.

01:07:07.040 --> 01:07:08.760
Now I have told you

01:07:08.960 --> 01:07:12.240
whether you forgive or you don’t forgive, you don’t do anything.

01:07:12.440 --> 01:07:14.080
But if you don’t forgive,

01:07:14.280 --> 01:07:16.560
then you play into wrong hands

01:07:16.760 --> 01:07:18.120
and torture yourself.

01:07:18.320 --> 01:07:21.920
Especially at this moment, you should forgive

01:07:22.120 --> 01:07:25.960
all of them, without thinking about them, in general,

01:07:26.160 --> 01:07:29.520
so that your center opens out.

01:07:29.720 --> 01:07:33.840
Otherwise at this important moment,

01:07:34.040 --> 01:07:36.680
you may miss your Self Realization.

01:07:36.880 --> 01:07:38.360
It's very important

01:07:38.560 --> 01:07:42.560
to forgive all of them from your heart.

01:07:42.760 --> 01:07:46.000
Not how many times, it's not the point, from your heart.

01:07:46.200 --> 01:07:47.840
So now please put your right hand

01:07:48.040 --> 01:07:49.800
on you forehead across

01:07:50.000 --> 01:07:56.080
and bend your head as much as you can.

01:07:56.280 --> 01:07:59.720
And here,

01:07:59.920 --> 01:08:04.000
you have to say,

01:08:04.200 --> 01:08:09.400
not how many times, but from your heart,

01:08:09.600 --> 01:08:15.840
“Mother, I forgive everyone in general”,

01:08:16.040 --> 01:08:19.960
from your heart. Please say it from your heart.

01:08:34.040 --> 01:08:35.520
And now

01:08:35.720 --> 01:08:39.040
please put your right hand on the back side of your head

01:08:39.240 --> 01:08:46.800
and push back your head as far as possible.

01:08:47.000 --> 01:08:49.160
Here, without feeling guilty,

01:08:49.360 --> 01:08:51.120
without counting your mistakes,

01:08:51.320 --> 01:08:54.200
just for your satisfaction,

01:08:54.400 --> 01:08:55.480
you have to say,

01:08:55.680 --> 01:09:00.520
not how many times, but from your heart,

01:09:00.720 --> 01:09:02.560
“Oh, Divine Power,

01:09:02.760 --> 01:09:07.640
if I have done any mistake,

01:09:07.840 --> 01:09:11.720
knowingly or unknowingly, please forgive me”.

01:09:11.920 --> 01:09:13.920
Just say it from your heart.

01:09:14.120 --> 01:09:15.640
“O Divine Power,

01:09:15.800 --> 01:09:19.480
if I have done anything wrong,

01:09:19.680 --> 01:09:24.400
knowingly or unknowingly, please forgive me”.

01:09:32.560 --> 01:09:34.680
Now

01:09:34.880 --> 01:09:38.760
please stretch your palms.

01:09:38.960 --> 01:09:40.760
Put the center of your palm

01:09:40.960 --> 01:09:44.200
on top of your fontanel bone area

01:09:44.400 --> 01:09:48.520
which is a soft bone in your childhood.

01:09:48.720 --> 01:09:50.040
Here again,

01:09:50.240 --> 01:09:54.320
I cannot force Self-Realization on you. You have to ask for it.

01:09:54.520 --> 01:09:57.280
So now push back your fingers - that's important -

01:09:57.480 --> 01:10:00.240
and please put down your head.

01:10:00.480 --> 01:10:03.400
Now move your scalp with this pressure,

01:10:03.600 --> 01:10:06.280
seven times, saying

01:10:06.480 --> 01:10:07.880
seven times,

01:10:08.080 --> 01:10:12.920
“Mother, please give me my Self-Realization”,

01:10:13.120 --> 01:10:15.640
because I cannot force it on you.

01:10:19.760 --> 01:10:21.800
Please push back your fingers.

01:10:22.000 --> 01:10:26.480
Bend your heads; please push back your fingers.

01:10:30.160 --> 01:10:32.000
Keep your eyes shut, till I tell you

01:10:32.200 --> 01:10:34.480
please keep them shut.

01:11:03.920 --> 01:11:07.160
Please take down your hands

01:11:07.360 --> 01:11:12.000
and try to open your eyes slowly.

01:11:12.200 --> 01:11:16.440
Push both the hands towards Me.

01:11:21.840 --> 01:11:22.880
Now,

01:11:23.120 --> 01:11:26.360
put the left hand towards Me like this,

01:11:26.560 --> 01:11:30.200
bend your head and see with the right hand

01:11:30.400 --> 01:11:36.480
if there is a cool or a warm breeze-like energy

01:11:36.680 --> 01:11:39.960
is coming out of your fontanel bone area.

01:11:40.200 --> 01:11:43.920
Now don’t doubt, because air conditioning is not in your head.

01:11:44.120 --> 01:11:48.560
So just see for yourself. Some people think it is air conditioning.

01:11:51.680 --> 01:11:54.040
Some people get it hot.

01:11:54.240 --> 01:11:56.320
Some people get it far,

01:11:56.520 --> 01:11:57.560
some closer,

01:11:57.760 --> 01:12:00.800
but don’t put your hand on top of your head,

01:12:01.000 --> 01:12:02.280
away from it.

01:12:02.480 --> 01:12:03.840
See for yourself,

01:12:04.040 --> 01:12:07.240
and if it is hot, that means you have not yet forgiven.

01:12:07.440 --> 01:12:09.480
So please forgive also.

01:12:09.680 --> 01:12:11.120
Now,

01:12:11.320 --> 01:12:14.280
please put your right hand. Now, bend your head nicely

01:12:14.480 --> 01:12:17.120
and see for yourself with the left hand

01:12:17.320 --> 01:12:23.320
if there's a cool or a hot breeze-like energy is coming

01:12:23.520 --> 01:12:28.560
out of your fontanel bone area.

01:12:28.760 --> 01:12:33.640
You have to move your hand up and down, sideways also. All right.

01:12:33.840 --> 01:12:38.080
Now do it with the left hand again.

01:12:42.560 --> 01:12:44.640
Little further. Some people get it further.

01:12:44.840 --> 01:12:50.160
Bend your heads, that is important, bend your heads.

01:12:51.960 --> 01:12:54.760
Now,

01:12:54.960 --> 01:12:59.040
please put both your hands towards the sky.

01:12:59.240 --> 01:13:01.080
Push back your head

01:13:01.280 --> 01:13:04.040
and ask anyone of these three questions,

01:13:04.240 --> 01:13:06.840
three times, anyone of them.

01:13:07.040 --> 01:13:08.960
You can say, ”Mother,

01:13:09.160 --> 01:13:13.040
is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?”,

01:13:13.240 --> 01:13:16.000
or ”Mother, is this the

01:13:16.200 --> 01:13:19.920
All Pervading Power of Divine Love?”,

01:13:20.120 --> 01:13:24.160
or ”Mother, is this the Ruh

01:13:24.360 --> 01:13:25.560
or Paramchaitanya?”.

01:13:25.760 --> 01:13:29.360
Ask anyone of these questions, three times.

01:13:35.920 --> 01:13:39.720
Now, just come down.

01:13:43.840 --> 01:13:46.680
Now please put your hands like this

01:13:46.880 --> 01:13:50.120
and watch Me without thinking.

01:13:50.320 --> 01:13:53.840
Just watch Me without thinking.

01:14:04.680 --> 01:14:07.680
All those who have felt

01:14:07.880 --> 01:14:11.480
hot or cold breeze on their fingertips,

01:14:11.680 --> 01:14:17.720
on their palms or out of their fontanel bone area,

01:14:17.920 --> 01:14:20.080
please raise both your hands.

01:14:22.480 --> 01:14:25.960
My God! Look at that.

01:14:26.200 --> 01:14:28.480
I mean most of you.

01:14:28.680 --> 01:14:29.840
May God bless you!

01:14:30.040 --> 01:14:31.520
It's tremendous.

01:14:31.720 --> 01:14:34.160
Some didn’t get it, very few,

01:14:34.360 --> 01:14:36.840
but most of you have got it.

01:14:37.040 --> 01:14:39.960
In any case all of you should get it.

01:14:40.160 --> 01:14:42.200
And those who haven’t got

01:14:42.400 --> 01:14:46.280
should please later on come to the stage and they will do it.

01:14:46.480 --> 01:14:47.760
But in the meanwhile

01:14:47.960 --> 01:14:49.560
we'll try something else

01:14:49.760 --> 01:14:52.440
for Realization

01:14:52.640 --> 01:14:55.080
and maybe that might help a little bit.

01:14:55.280 --> 01:14:57.960
[Marathi].

01:14:58.160 --> 01:15:01.880
See this might help.

01:15:06.440 --> 01:15:09.360
This will be only five minutes experiment. Let's see.

01:15:09.560 --> 01:15:12.280
Which song will you sing?

01:15:12.480 --> 01:15:14.480
[Marathi].

01:15:17.360 --> 01:15:20.560
[Marathi].

01:15:20.760 --> 01:15:22.960
This is the song they are going to sing,

01:15:23.160 --> 01:15:26.120
was written - Namadeva -

01:15:26.320 --> 01:15:28.760
by Namadeva in the sixteenth century

01:15:28.960 --> 01:15:31.760
who went then to Punjab

01:15:31.960 --> 01:15:34.760
and Guru Nanak Sahib, you see,

01:15:34.960 --> 01:15:38.600
knew who he was and He asked him to write

01:15:38.800 --> 01:15:41.120
poems in Punjabi language.

01:15:41.320 --> 01:15:45.000
And he has done such big compilation, I know that.

01:15:45.240 --> 01:15:47.480
This guru

01:15:47.680 --> 01:15:48.960
was ...

01:15:49.160 --> 01:15:51.240
he was just a tailor.

01:15:51.440 --> 01:15:53.520
And he went to see, meet

01:15:53.720 --> 01:15:57.960
another realized soul who was a potter.

01:16:00.560 --> 01:16:04.320
And when he went and saw the potter kneading

01:16:04.520 --> 01:16:11.920
the clay with his feet, he just stood there, watching him.

01:16:12.120 --> 01:16:14.880
The potter’s name was Gora Kumbhar.

01:16:15.080 --> 01:16:19.120
Looked at him and what does he say,

01:16:19.320 --> 01:16:22.880
in Marathi says that, but meaning

01:16:23.080 --> 01:16:27.000
that, I came to see here

01:16:27.200 --> 01:16:28.960
the "formless",

01:16:29.200 --> 01:16:32.120
but it is "in the form".

01:16:32.320 --> 01:16:34.120
I see it "in the form".

01:16:34.320 --> 01:16:40.880
I mean only a saint can say it to another saint.

01:16:41.080 --> 01:16:42.440
That’s what happened

01:16:42.640 --> 01:16:46.080
that he went up to Punjab

01:16:46.280 --> 01:16:49.360
where Guru Nanak Sahib

01:16:49.560 --> 01:16:53.560
called him, looked after him and asked him and they made beautiful,

01:16:53.760 --> 01:16:58.040
I mean such beautiful songs there are and they are in Granth Sahib.

01:16:58.240 --> 01:17:01.800
They are all in Granth Sahib.

01:17:03.400 --> 01:17:04.680
[unclear].

01:17:04.880 --> 01:17:06.320
This is the folk song

01:17:06.520 --> 01:17:11.240
which was written, which says, “Oh, Mother, give me my Realization.

01:17:11.440 --> 01:17:14.440
‘Jogwa’ means Yoga - "Please give me that".

01:17:14.640 --> 01:17:15.960
All that they sang,

01:17:16.200 --> 01:17:18.320
all the time they have been singing, even now,

01:17:18.520 --> 01:17:20.360
but they don’t know what it is.

01:17:20.560 --> 01:17:23.280
And they are saying, "Oh, Ambe" - means the Kundalini -

01:17:23.480 --> 01:17:25.280
"please rise, rise".

01:17:25.480 --> 01:17:29.280
And with you can also clap. It will help a lot, I am sure.

01:17:29.480 --> 01:17:34.000
This will definitely consolidate your Self-Realization.

01:17:38.920 --> 01:17:42.400
It is a village song. It’s a rustic...

01:26:27.500 --> 01:26:31.160
Now you feel. Just try to feel now. Let's see.

01:26:31.360 --> 01:26:35.600
You must be feeling more, just see.

01:26:35.800 --> 01:26:37.120
All right?

01:26:37.320 --> 01:26:39.960
Now again, let us see how many of you have really

01:26:40.160 --> 01:26:42.400
felt on your finger tips

01:26:42.600 --> 01:26:47.160
or from your fontanel bone area or on your palms.

01:26:47.360 --> 01:26:51.400
Raise your both the hands.

01:26:51.600 --> 01:26:57.400
Oh! So, who didn’t feel before, have felt it - so many of you.

01:26:57.600 --> 01:27:00.960
Thank you very much. May God look after you.

01:27:01.160 --> 01:27:03.600
And also have wisdom

01:27:03.800 --> 01:27:08.200
to respect your freedom,

01:27:08.400 --> 01:27:14.560
respect your new status.

01:27:14.760 --> 01:27:17.880
The real freedom is now.

01:27:18.080 --> 01:27:22.280
So you respect your Self-Realization

01:27:22.480 --> 01:27:29.880
and become a fully self-realized personality.

01:27:30.080 --> 01:27:33.600
That will help everywhere.

01:27:33.800 --> 01:27:38.320
May God bless you all!

01:27:40.240 --> 01:27:44.360
Thank you very much, it was wonderful.

01:28:19.880 --> 01:28:23.920
You all have paper to know where the centers are

01:28:24.160 --> 01:28:26.840
and I hope...

01:28:27.040 --> 01:28:28.720
What's it?

01:28:28.920 --> 01:28:31.240
...and where you are going to have

01:28:31.440 --> 01:28:35.000
a follow-on program.

01:28:35.200 --> 01:28:37.800
All right?

01:28:38.000 --> 01:28:40.120
Please, please come.

01:28:40.560 --> 01:28:43.200
Do you know?

01:28:43.400 --> 01:28:45.520
What's it? They haven’t got paper already?

01:28:45.720 --> 01:28:46.960
SY: They have, Shri Mataji.

01:28:47.160 --> 01:28:49.200
SM: They all have?

01:28:49.440 --> 01:28:51.040
Where are you having follow on?

01:28:52.120 --> 01:28:55.840
Yes, yes, but when are having the follow on, where?

01:28:56.040 --> 01:29:00.280
You don't know.

01:29:00.480 --> 01:29:02.680
SY: As you go on out

01:29:02.880 --> 01:29:06.000
there are leaflets there which will tell you...

01:29:06.240 --> 01:29:08.240
all you need to know about follow-up programs.

01:29:08.440 --> 01:29:12.080
Ah, we've got one here, finally.

01:29:16.200 --> 01:29:17.960
There's a series of seven programs

01:29:18.160 --> 01:29:20.720
beginning on Monday 11th of April

01:29:20.920 --> 01:29:25.360
then for six consecutive Thursdays commencing

01:29:25.560 --> 01:29:27.600
Thursday 14th of April

01:29:27.800 --> 01:29:30.680
at seven thirty to nine thirty

01:29:30.880 --> 01:29:33.600
the [Far placed Room], Gorman House Art Center

01:29:33.800 --> 01:29:36.720
Ainslie Avenue, Braddon.

01:29:38.320 --> 01:29:41.000
And there's a little bracket here, and we will provide

01:29:41.200 --> 01:29:44.000
light refreshments to follow.

01:29:47.280 --> 01:29:50.480
Again remind you that all Sahaja Yoga programs

01:29:50.680 --> 01:29:54.160
are completely free.

01:29:54.360 --> 01:29:59.320
There, if you have any questions you want to ask about that

01:29:59.520 --> 01:30:02.440
there's two phone numbers here that

01:30:02.640 --> 01:30:04.560
will tell you where to ring.

01:30:04.760 --> 01:30:06.760
It really tells you everything you want to know

01:30:06.960 --> 01:30:08.800
and you can pick up one of these up

01:30:08.960 --> 01:30:10.080
as you go out the door.

01:30:10.280 --> 01:30:12.760
Now they've got a big supply there.

01:30:24.200 --> 01:30:26.120
One other thing, if is anybody here

01:30:26.320 --> 01:30:28.720
who - as soon as Shri Mataji's left -

01:30:28.920 --> 01:30:32.320
if there's anybody here who has not felt anything tonight,

01:30:32.520 --> 01:30:34.080
I would like to try.

01:30:34.280 --> 01:30:38.120
There's probably a very good reasons, as we explained to you earlier.

01:30:38.320 --> 01:30:41.880
You have these centers - you can also have blocked centers -

01:30:42.080 --> 01:30:45.520
they may be quite easily to clear, might be quite easy to clear and then

01:30:45.720 --> 01:30:47.000
[unclear].

01:30:47.200 --> 01:30:48.720
Before you leave here tonight

01:30:48.920 --> 01:30:50.840
if are any of you didn't feel anything

01:30:51.040 --> 01:30:54.960
we'll do our best to make sure you do.

01:30:55.200 --> 01:30:57.600
Thank you.

01:31:18.120 --> 01:31:22.760
We're having first series of seven follow up programs

01:31:23.080 --> 01:31:25.920
at Gorman House.
